{"tid":515108,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"干地回顧2017：偉大的一年","createTime":"2017-12-31T07:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T07:11:30.000Z","uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7bd007ec37fe84d4f412a4025fe086704a6e66f4","tid":515108,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=C7bob7MPBLmiGh%2F7fkw9dfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=953fb3ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周六英超，車路士於2017年最後一場比賽，主場以5:0血洗史篤城，領隊干地認為今年算得上豐收。<br />\n<br />\n以勝利為2017年作結，干地（Antonio Conte）坦言：「對球會、球迷、球員、我自己來說，我們完成了偉大的一年。我首次於這聯賽作戰就捧走冠軍，不是一件容易的事，所以我要感謝球會給予我機會。」<br />\n<br />\n說到今場收起翼鋒夏薩特及中場法比加斯，干地坦言為了保持球員狀態而輪換：「1月很多比賽，2月歐聯重開，所以我需要所有球員都保持最佳狀態。」對於增兵，他表示：「我跟球會傾談過，他們知道我的意見。」<br />\n<br />\n今夏加盟後，在周六終於開齋的真禾特（Danny Drinkwater）說：「我為這個入球感到快樂，建功的感覺真的很好。現在我們可以用今場勝利，去為下場鬥阿仙奴建立信心。爭標夢仍然未完，我們要繼續贏波。」"},{"pid":"0674ed2c416ac8c1ef3140e27ab4803a26a1215c","tid":515108,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"畀獌聯騎住都偉大?"},{"pid":"67d448ecdd6c97f7e154328e2cb3681efd4efd87","tid":515108,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T07:08:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畀獌聯騎住都偉大?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6370d942b7060e81ba3a234ddc45306b996258","tid":515108,"uid":138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0674ed2c416ac8c1ef3140e27ab4803a26a1215c","tid":515108,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"畀獌聯騎住都偉大?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"唔好再講 好撚無面"},{"pid":"75eb526f1b1ecc8e4e23043d1cb224e0d01b2105","tid":515108,"uid":93220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67d448ecdd6c97f7e154328e2cb3681efd4efd87","tid":515108,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep